19. Qb3 {White's position is somewhat preferable due to the powerful Nd4,
though Black is very solid.}) 9... O-O 10. O-O Nc6 (10... Bb7 11. Nbd2 Nc6 12.
Rc1 Qb6 13. Nb3 Ne4 14. Ne5 Rfd8 15. Be3 $1 $14 {secured c5 for the knight and
