11. Ne5 $1 {The knight enters the centre in time.} ({Less energetic is} 11.
Nbd2 Bf5 12. Nb3 Ne4 13. Rc1 Rc8 {with approximately equal chances.}) 11... Bb7
12. Nxc6 Bxc6 13. Be5 e6 ({I've examined the following typical idea:} 13... a5
