Nd2 e6 18. Nb3 $14) 14. Nd2 Bh6 15. Rc1 {This forces Black to put his queen's
rook on c8.} ({After} 15. e3 Qe7 16. h4 b4 17. Qc2 Rfc8 18. Rfc1 Bd7 {Black
