16. e3 $1 {This natural move is a certain improvement} ({over} 16. Bxf6 Qxf6
17. e3 b4 $1 18. Re1 Qd8 19. Bf1 Qb6 20. Nf3 Rc7 21. Qd3 Ra8 {was equal in
