) ({Black does not achieve much by attacking the queen with the knight:} 10...
Nb6 11. Qc2 Nfd5 12. Rd1 (12. e4 {is now somewhat premature in view of} Nb4 13.
Qd2 Nc4 14. Qd1 Bg4 15. a3 Na6 $132 {Figlio,G - Jijon,F ICCF email 2011}) 12...
Nxc3 (12... Nb4 13. Qb1 Qd7 ({Even worse is} 13... Bf5 14. e4 Bg4 15. h3 Bxf3
16. Bxf3 Qd7 17. a3 Na6 18. Bg4 e6 19. e5 $16 {Klein, E-Gulevich,A email 2008})
14. a3 N4d5 15. Ne4 {Black did not manage to solve his space problems in the
