Bxe5 $11) 10... Na5 ({The attempt to simplify the matters through} 10... e4
11. dxc6 Qxd1 12. Rxd1 exf3 13. Bxf3 bxc6 {does not seem to work because of}
14. Bd2 $1 {White's main task is completing the development and releasing
