, as was played in a dozen of games can be strongly met by} Bg4 $1 $146 16. f3
Be6 17. Nxc7 Bc4 {, and Black has sufficient compensation for 2 pawns.})
14... Nc4 15. Na4 Rb8 (15... Bf5 16. Rac1 Ne5 17. Be2 $16 {Black had no
