This somewhat passive move is the best.} (19... cxd4 $6 20. Bxb4 Re8
({After} 20... dxe3 21. Bxf8 exf2+ 22. Kh1 Qxf8 23. Rb1 {White is better, but
it was the lesser evil.}) 21. Rc1 Nb7 {This position took place in Simek, P -
